      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare opportunity for a serious collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original showroom shine without a single scratch or blemish. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. The interior remains in pristine, like-new condition, showing no signs of wear.",
